title: Partnered Universities
subheading: We proudly collaborate with top universities worldwide, connecting you with leading institutions that match your academic goals. Explore a wide range of programs with trusted partners for a successful study abroad experience!

items.title: Britts Imperial University College
items.description:
Committed Student Consultancy is an authorized partner of Britts Imperial University College, UAE, dedicated to supporting Bangladeshi students and others in achieving their educational aspirations abroad. Through this partnership, we provide direct access to Britts Imperial’s wide-ranging academic programs and international opportunities, spanning the UK, USA, Europe, and Australia.

With our guidance, students benefit from a seamless admission process, from program selection to visa support, ensuring they have a smooth transition to studying in the UAE. This partnership also offers flexible options like credit transfer opportunities, where students can begin their studies at Britts Imperial and have the chance to transfer credits to partner universities globally.

Our team offers priority application processing, personalized academic advice, and ongoing support, enabling students to focus on their educational goals. Committed Student Consultancy and Britts Imperial University College are united in providing an empowering educational pathway for students seeking a rewarding international experience.

items.title: Nest Academy
items.description:
Committed Student Consultancy is an authorized partner of Nest Academy in Dubai, offering Bangladeshi students and others a unique opportunity to pursue quality education in the heart of the UAE. Nest Academy is known for its specialized programs in fields like Sports Management, Events Management, Business, and Computing, tailored to meet industry demands and equip students with practical skills for thriving careers.
Through this partnership, Committed Student Consultancy provides direct guidance on admissions, program selection, and visa support, ensuring students have a clear, supportive pathway to studying in Dubai. We also facilitate credit transfer options, allowing students the flexibility to begin their studies at Nest Academy and explore further educational opportunities.
With priority application processing and personalized support, Committed Student Consultancy helps students seamlessly transition to academic life in Dubai, empowering them to achieve their educational and professional ambitions in an international environment.

items.title: EWVS- Australia
items.description:
Committed Student Consultancy is an authorized partner of EWVS in Australia, opening doors for Bangladeshi students and others to access world-class education and career opportunities. Through this partnership, we offer a direct pathway to Australian institutions, providing students with access to diverse programs across fields and specializations.

Our partnership with EWVS ensures a comprehensive, guided application experience, from selecting the right program to visa assistance and post-admission support. Students benefit from flexible study options, including potential credit transfers that allow them to start their studies in Australia and explore further academic opportunities.

Committed Student Consultancy provides priority processing, personalized guidance, and ongoing support to ensure a smooth transition to student life in Australia. Together, we empower students with quality education choices and a clear route to international academic and career success.

items.title: Guizhou University
items.description: As an authorized partner of Guizhou University, we connect students with leading agriculture, environmental science, and engineering programs. Our team ensures smooth admission, visa support, and guidance for a successful study experience in China.

items.title: HBUT
items.description: Committed Student Consultancy partners with HBUT, offering students access to top programs in engineering, technology, and business. We provide full admission support, visa assistance, and flexible credit transfers to start your studies in China seamlessly.

items.title: Committed College
items.description: Committed Student Consultancy partners with CSC College to provide students with quality education opportunities tailored to their career goals. We offer full support with admissions, program selection, and visa assistance, helping students make a confident start to their academic journey. With CSC College, students gain practical skills and industry-ready knowledge in a supportive, career-focused environment.
